---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — propernet.ca"
  description="Privacy policy for propernet.ca — how we handle your personal information."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 font-heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4 font-heading">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        When you submit our consultation form, we collect the information you provide — including your name, email address, phone number, and details about your home and network needs. This information is sent to us via Web3Forms and delivered to our email.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4 font-heading">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We use your information solely to respond to your consultation request, provide quotes, and deliver our services. We do not sell, share, or rent your personal information to third parties.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4 font-heading">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our contact form uses <a href="https://web3forms.com" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Web3Forms</a> to process submissions. Your form data is transmitted through their service and delivered to our email. We encourage you to review their privacy policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4 font-heading">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We retain your contact information only as long as necessary to fulfill your request and provide our services. You can request deletion of your data at any time by emailing us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4 font-heading">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@propernet.ca" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@propernet.ca</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
